1.0.name: wordpress/mass-page-remover
1.0.description:
Mass Page Remover does exactly what the name implies: it makes it very easy to remove as many pages as you want.

The plugin works as an admin panel. The form contains a start page ID and an end page ID as well as an input for specific IDs.

Please provide feedback on the blog post so that I can improve the plugin further.

For a complete list of the changes from each version, please visit the plugin homepage.

For examples and tips on using the plugin, please check the examples on the plugin homepage.

Be sure to check out my other plugins at my Wordpress profile.

USAGE

  1. After activating the plugin, navigate to the admin panel interface, where the options can be entered to remove the required number
